    public class UserChannelDao<U extends User,C extends Channel>
extends Object
implements Closeable
    Stores and maintains relationships between users and channels. This class should not be directly, it is meant to be the internal storage engine.

      • getAllUsers

        public com.google.common.collect.ImmutableSortedSet<U> getAllUsers()
        Get all user's in the channel. There are some important things to note about this method:
        • This method may not return a full list of users if you call it before the complete nick list has arrived from the IRC server.
        • If you wish to find out which users are in a channel as soon as you join it, then you should listen for a UserListEvent instead of calling this method, as the UserListEvent is only dispatched as soon as the full user list has been received.
        • This method will return immediately, as it does not require any interaction with the IRC server.
        Parameters:
        chan - The channel object to search in
        Returns:
        A Set of all user's in the channel
        Since:
        PircBot 1.0.0
        See Also:
        UserListEvent
